{
  "texts": [
    "Let's think step by step.",
    "Rong has been saving 20 coins per month for 10 years, so he has saved a total of 20 x 10 = 200 coins.",
    "Neil has been saving 2/5 times more coins than Rong, so he has saved 2/5 x 20 = 40 coins per month.",
    "He has saved a total of 40 x 10 = 400 coins.",
    "Therefore, Rong has 200 coins and Neil has 400 coins after 10 years of saving.\""
  ]
}